                    <h3>Life lately in poem</h3>
                    <div class="poem-verse">
                        <p>Berlin hums in neon blues,</p>
                        <p>trams sigh along the empty avenues,</p>
                        <p>I wake to rain tapping on glass,</p>
                        <p>another day, another class.</p>
                    </div>
                   

                    <div class="poem-verse-right">
                        <p>Code flickers on my screen like static,</p>
                        <p>functions, loops—it´s all mathematics,</p>
                        <p>but somewhere in the syntax maze,</p>
                        <p>I find a rhythm, a kind of grace.</p>
                    </div>
                    

                    <div class="poem-verse">
                        <p>Nights stretch long in Kreuzberg bars,</p>
                        <p>where strangers laugh beneath the stars,</p>
                        <p>and though I sit among the crowd,</p>
                        <p class="highlight">somehow silence feels too loud.</p> 
                    </div>

                    <div class="poem-verse-right">
                        <p>Then Canada—snow and open sky,</p>
                        <p>a place to breathe, a place to try,</p>
                        <p>guitar strings hum beneath my hand,</p>
                        <p>songs of love I’d never planned.</p>
                    </div>


                    <div class="poem-verse">
                        <p>She laughed like spring, her touch like fire,</p>
                        <p>a moment brief, a world entire,</p>
                        <p>but love’s a train that never stays,</p>
                        <p>just echoes down the alleyways.</p>
                    </div>


                    <div class="poem-verse-right">
                        <p>Now back in Berlin, alone but whole,</p>
                        <p>chasing dreams that burn the soul,</p>
                        <p>the city moves, the future calls—</p>
                        <p class="highlight">I stand, I learn, I risk it all.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
